African Development Bank, Denmark Set Up $57 Million Energy Fund

-- B y   J i h e n   L a g h m a r i
-- 
2011-07-17T11:56:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/african-development-bank-denmark-set-up-57-million-energy-fund.html
The  African Development Bank  signed
an agreement with  Denmark  to establish a 300-million Danish
krone ($57 million) sustainable energy fund for  Africa , the
Tunis-based bank said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jihen Laghmari in Cairo at 
 jlaghmari@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mahmoud Kassem at 
 mkassem1@bloomberg.net . 